              {
                "lang_tag": "ui7_kitdevice_2074_step3",
                "text": "Turn the scroll wheel to the L position. Press down on the wheel to begin the pairing process.<br/><br/><b>Note</b>: You may need to first 'wake up' the thermostat by moving the wheel to the <b>n</b> symbol and pressing on it. The thermostat will confirm it is awake by displaying the <b>nP</b> symbol."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "static_group": 2,
            "group_text": [
              {
                "lang_tag": "ui7_kitdevice_2074_step4",
                "text": "When the thermostat is paired the screen will display <b>LP</b> and the antenna symbol above it will indicate it's connected to your Vera.<br/><br/>When pairing is completed, return Switch 1  to the OFF position. (IMPORTANT!)<br/><br/>If the Thermostat isn't detected in the next 60 seconds, then click the 'Retry' button below and begin the un-pairing process."
              }
            ]
          }
